{"tid":1884024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴動案夫婦派500罩助清潔工","createTime":"2020-02-17T10:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T13:04:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"29b8021f63e922ed9e0fcd47f72c66f5342c38e5","tid":1884024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/SCBMP2BL5RTZLSG6VYZCOWO56E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FSCBMP2BL5RTZLSG6VYZCOWO56E%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbJzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=52ec4218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FSCBMP2BL5RTZLSG6VYZCOWO56E%2F&h=4806b2ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/SCBMP2BL5RTZLSG6VYZCOWO56E/</a><br />\n<br />\n暴動案夫婦派500罩助清潔工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200217/large/1581870009_80f8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200217%2Flarge%2F1581870009_80f8.gif&h=4d7da56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湯偉雄及杜依蘭遊走西環的垃圾站派口罩予基層人士。何賢攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有醫學組織聯會專家呼籲健康的人士不用戴口罩，然而此說法未能為坊間的口罩荒降珉，昨日仍有購買口罩的人龍，基層人士更要捱貴價口罩。被控暴動罪的新婚夫婦湯偉雄、杜依蘭，昨日連同友人在上環及附近一帶垃圾收集站派口罩予清潔工人，希望能減輕一點他們的負擔，「希望每個人都可以做多啲，盡自己嘅力量去幫助一班基層市民」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：任職跨國建築師樓  全體員工留家一周<br />\n<br />\n心痛基層不受保障<br />\n<br />\n夫婦二人發揮朋友圈的力量，用四天眾籌了500多個N95及外科口罩，昨日在西環附近的垃圾站派發予清潔工人。<br />\n<br />\n在遊走各垃圾站期間，他們發現有清潔工人操尼泊爾口音，又聽不懂廣東話，湯偉雄感嘆他們的需求經常被社會忽略。二人說，基層人士未必不關心政治，但可能由於他們需要維持基本的生活需要，「畀人分為藍」，「唔好因為一個疫情令到佢哋好驚，一個黃藍陣營（區分不同人）變相剝削一班應該受關注嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n有清潔工人透露，僱主每天只會給予員工一個口罩，惟他們通常一天需工作10小時，而且經常接觸垃圾及洗地等的高危工作，口罩的防禦力未必能支撐一天的工作量。<br />\n<br />\n上年7月28日，湯偉雄及杜依蘭在德輔道西近西邊街一帶被捕，其後被控一項暴動罪。為何今次選擇以清潔工人為派口罩的對象，湯偉雄解釋，外判清潔工人往往不受勞工法例保障，有清潔工人在工作期間戴上「超薄口罩」，又要捱天價口罩，他感到痛心，「一來呢班工人工時長，二來就算佢哋知道（有賣口罩的地方）都未必會排得到」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者何嘉瑤"},{"pid":"d77e59a38a3193e074da9a02596d5f788f2e2774","tid":1884024,"uid":49643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"好人有好報"},{"pid":"162802b78cced2712fc5743d86c683193d218aa8","tid":1884024,"uid":47208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"好人有好報"},{"pid":"3db2a98f1999f423d589f9bc2211456bc178adb8","tid":1884024,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"真香港人"},{"pid":"fb4da0586012cd42f65a72ca61c5180bca8adb19","tid":1884024,"uid":61974,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"呢批清潔工分分鐘藍絲，屌鳩抗爭者加重佢地負擔"},{"pid":"7842a6c13f1808af835892a77049d2abba38026b","tid":1884024,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32575105dcbeff7509af351cb9ac34cc62aaf3c3","tid":1884024,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"CC台：嬲到震，要同佢哋割席"},{"pid":"05992a7819763f081dd61c87c9b28a3f57d79b21","tid":1884024,"uid":230911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e875554a09371d8736ba361e94692afc66a6826","tid":1884024,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e26a4bd3a3b4fc974f90f718aec5657890624f","tid":1884024,"uid":59693,"like":0,"disl